snippet.title: Fiddlebert's Folly (Pikmin Direct!)
snippet.description:
This is a mod I've been working on for the past 5 months. I'm a single developer who really likes Fiddlebert! So I've decided to make him his own story! No, this is not a joke mod, I really am putting my all into this goofy hack.

Song by Vivvy Boy:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JNwR1dusULw
